OL,3,CFood producer being sued over alleged
OL,4,C'chicken farm pollution' of River Wye
OL,6,FOne of the UK's biggest food producers
OL,7,Fis being sued for allegedly damaging
OL,8,Fthe River Wye.
OL,10,FLaw firm Leigh Day claims that
OL,11,Findustrial-scale chicken farming in
OL,12,FHerefordshire, supplying Avara Foods,
OL,13,Fhas been the overwhelming cause of
OL,14,Fphosphorous pollution in the river.
OL,16,FThe River Wye flows for 150 miles,
OL,17,Flargely along the border of England
OL,18,Fand Wales.
