OL,3,CFood producer being sued over alleged
OL,4,C'chicken farm pollution' of River Wye
OL,6,FPoultry production in the area has
OL,7,Fexpanded rapidly in recent years, with
OL,8,Faround 23 million birds being produced
OL,9,Fin the River Wye catchment area at any
OL,10,Fone time.
OL,12,FAvara said it has published a plan to
OL,13,Fensure chicken farms in its supply
OL,14,Fchain no longer contribute excess
OL,15,Fphosphate into the River Wye.
