OL,3,CFood producer being sued over alleged
OL,4,C'chicken farm pollution' of River Wye
OL,6,FThe solicitors say the company - which
OL,7,Fsupplies Tesco - is responsible for
OL,8,Fthe existing damage and was being sued
OL,9,Fon behalf of people living in the Wye
OL,10,Fcatchment who have been impacted by
OL,11,Friver pollution.
OL,13,FThe law firm says the deterioration of
OL,14,Fthe Wye has damaged the lives and
OL,15,Flivelihoods of people living in the
OL,16,Farea, including swimmers, canoeists,
OL,17,Fwalkers and anglers.
