OL,3,CFood producer being sued over alleged
OL,4,C'chicken farm pollution' of River Wye
OL,6,FPartner at Leigh Day, Oliver Holland,
OL,7,Fwho is handling the claim said: "This
OL,8,Fdestruction of one of the UK's most
OL,9,Fbeautiful natural areas cannot
OL,10,Fcontinue, which is why we are bringing
OL,11,Flegal action."
OL,13,FCampaigners from River Action said:
OL,14,F"It is entirely appropriate that the
OL,15,Fpolluter must now be made to pay to
OL,16,Fclean up the mess we believe it has
OL,17,Fcreated and subsequently profited
OL,18,Ffrom."
OL,20,F, in separate legal action.
