OL,3,CFood producer being sued over alleged
OL,4,C'chicken farm pollution' of River Wye
OL,6,F, the government's nature watchdog,
OL,7,Fafter a decline in Atlantic salmon.
OL,9,FLawyers from Leigh Day say that
OL,10,Findustrial-scale chicken farming is
OL,11,Fgenerating significant quantities of
OL,12,Fphosphorus-rich manure, which is
OL,13,Frunning into the soil and the river.
OL,15,FThey claim that this is raising
OL,16,Fphosphorous levels in the water, which
OL,17,Fis causing algal blooms leading to
OL,18,Fbiodiversity loss and a reduction in
OL,19,Fwater quality.
