OL,6,FThousands of people living in the area
OL,7,Faround the River Wye could share
OL,8,Fhundreds of millions of pounds in
OL,9,Fcompensation if the legal claim is
OL,10,Fsuccessful.
OL,12,FA spokesperson from Avara Food said
OL,13,Fthe claim had "no merit" and they are
OL,14,Fconfident "there is no case to defend".
